metadata.name: Levia Oel - NOX Angel of Peace
metadata.description:
Levia Oel's ascent during the blossom sakura was a magnificent sight to behold. As she soared through the air, her wings radiated with an intense, awe-inspiring energy. Her presence exuded a profound sense of peace and calmness, calming even the most restless of minds. 

The beauty of the sakura blossoms was amplified by her presence, creating a stunning backdrop for her flight. Levia Oel's ascent was a reminder of the beauty and majesty of the celestial calm, a sight that left those who witnessed it in awe.
